# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the bankruptcy petition cases presented in hong kong down went ##.# percent to ### in september , according to the official receiver 's office of hong kong friday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (o / office
            :poss (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (r / receive-01)
                  :mod (o2 / official))
            :location (c / city
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Hong"
                        :op2 "Kong")))
      :ARG1 (g / go-01
            :ARG1 (c2 / case-03
                  :ARG1 (p2 / petition-01
                        :ARG1 (b / bankrupt-01))
                  :ARG1-of (p3 / present-01
                        :location c))
            :ARG4 (p4 / percent)
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :month 9)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the european union launched legal proceedings thursday against france over the awarding of a dlrs ### million contract to build and run a giant soccer stadium for the #### world cup final .
# ::alignments
(l / launch-01
      :ARG0 (u / union
            :mod (c / continent
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Europe")))
      :ARG1 (p / proceeding-02
            :ARG1 (c2 / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "France"))
            :ARG3 (a / award-01
                  :ARG1 (c3 / contract-02
                        :ARG1 (a2 / and
                              :op1 (b / build-01
                                    :ARG1 (s / stadium
                                          :mod (s2 / soccer)
                                          :mod (g / giant))
                                    :purpose (f / final
                                          :mod (g2 / game
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "World"
                                                      :op2 "Cup"))))
                              :op2 (r / run-01
                                    :ARG1 s))
                        :ARG2 c2
                        :ARG3 (m / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 10000000
                              :unit (d / dollar))))
            :ARG1-of (l2 / legal-02))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok senior diplomats and aid groups held a meeting in the north korean capital pyongyang friday as they scrambled to find out details about a massive train crash in the country 's northwest .
# ::alignments
(h / hold-04
      :ARG0 (a / and
            :op1 (p / person
                  :mod (s / senior)
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG2 (d / diplomat)))
            :op2 (g / group
                  :ARG0-of (a2 / aid-01)))
      :ARG1 (m / meet-03
            :ARG0 a)
      :location (c / city
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Pyongyang")
            :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c2 / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "North"
                              :op2 "Korea"))
                  :ARG2 (c3 / capital)))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday))
      :time (s2 / scramble-01
            :ARG0 a
            :ARG1 (f2 / find-out-03
                  :ARG0 a
                  :ARG1 (d3 / detail
                        :topic (c4 / crash-01
                              :ARG1 (t / train)
                              :mod (m2 / massive)
                              :location (n3 / northwest))))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok turkey said on friday it has made no change in its military positions in cyprus following harsh protests by greece and greek cyprus , who claimed turkey had bolstered its military presence in the long-divided island .

      :ARG0 (c / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Turkey"))

            :polarity -
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (p / position-01
                  :ARG1 c
                  :ARG2 (m / military)
                  :location (c3 / cyprus))
            :ARG1-of (f / follow-01
                  :ARG2 (p2 / protest-01
                        :ARG0 (a / and
                              :op1 (c4 / country
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Greece"))
                              :op2 (c5 / country
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Greek"
                                          :op2 "Cyprus"))
                              :ARG0-of (c6 / claim-01
                                    :ARG1 (b / bolster-01
                                          :ARG0 c
                                          :ARG1 (p3 / present-02
                                                :ARG1 c
                                                :ARG2 c3
                                                :mod (m2 / military)))))
                        :ARG1-of (h / harsh-02)))
            :time (d / date-entity
                  :weekday (f2 / friday))))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok nokia corp. , the world 's leading mobile phone maker , posted a #-percent drop in fourth-quarter earnings thursday , as higher sales of low-end handsets pushed down the average selling price .
# ::alignments
(p / post-01
      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Nokia"
                  :op2 "Corp.")
            :mod (c2 / company
                  :ARG0-of (m / make-01
                        :ARG1 (p2 / phone
                              :mod (m2 / mobile)))
                  :ARG0-of (l / lead-01)
                  :location (w / world)))
      :ARG1 (d / drop-01
            :ARG1 c
            :ARG2 (p3 / percentage-entity
                  :value 1)
            :ARG3 (e / earn-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :time (q / quarter
                        :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                              :value 4)))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t / thursday))
            :ARG1-of (c3 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (p4 / push-01
                        :ARG0 (s / sell-01
                              :ARG1 (h / handset
                                    :mod (h2 / high-02)
                                    :mod (e2 / end
                                          :ARG1-of (l2 / low-04))))
                        :ARG1 (t2 / thing
                              :ARG2-of (p5 / price-01
                                    :ARG1 (s2 / sell-01))
                              :ARG1-of (a / average-04))
                        :ARG2 (d3 / down)))))

                        :ARG1 (p / person
                              :ARG0-of (t2 / traffic-01
                                    :ARG1 (h2 / heroin))
                              :ARG1-of (c5 / convict-01)
                              :mod (n2 / nation
                                    :mod (c6 / country
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Britain"))))
                        :ARG2 (d / die-01))
                  :ARG2 p
                  :time (d2 / date-entity
                        :weekday (t3 / tuesday)))
            :ARG2 (c7 / commute-02
                  :ARG0 c2
                  :ARG1 s2
                  :ARG4 (ii / imprison-01
                        :ARG1 p
                        :ARG2 (l / life)))))

                                    :op1 "Kerman"))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Mikheil"
                  :op2 "Saakashvili")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Gorgia"))
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)))
      :ARG1 (s2 / seek-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (h2 / help-01
                  :ARG0 (w / world-region
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "West"))
                  :ARG1 (a / and
                        :op1 (o / oust-01
                              :ARG0 w
                              :ARG1 (p3 / person
                                    :ARG0-of (k / keep-01
                                          :ARG1 (p4 / peace))
                                    :mod (c2 / country
                                          :name (n4 / name
                                                :op1 "Russia")))
                              :ARG2 (r / region
                                    :ARG0-of (r2 / rebel-01)
                                    :location (c3 / country
                                          :name (n5 / name
                                                :op1 "Abkhazia"))))
                        :op2 (r3 / replace-01
                              :ARG0 w
                              :ARG1 p3
                              :ARG2 (f / force
                                    :mod (ii / international))))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday)))

# ::alignments
(a / accuse-01
      :ARG1 (j / junta
            :mod (m / military)
            :location (p / province
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Sierra"
                        :op2 "Leone")))
      :ARG2 (a2 / attack-01
            :ARG0 j
            :ARG1 (f / force
                  :ARG0-of (k / keep-01
                        :ARG1 (p2 / peace))
                  :location (w / world-region
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "West"
                              :op2 "Africa")))
            :ARG2 (g / gas
                  :mod (n3 / nerve)))
      :time (t / today))
